Class ClackData

java.lang.Object
data.ClackData
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
FileClackData, MessageClackData
public abstract class ClackData extends Object implements Serializable
This is an abstract class that all ClackData classes will inherit from. It implements the Serializable interface.
